==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cook
<hw>Cook</hw> <pr>(k⟦oomac⟧k)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Of imitative
origin.]</ety> <def>To make the noise of the cuckoo.</def> <mark>[Obs.
or R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Constant cuckoos <qex>cook</qex> on every side.</q> <rj><qau>The
Silkworms (1599).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cook</ent>⟦br⟧

