<hw>Cook</hw> <pr>(k⟦oocr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To prepare food
for the table.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cookbook</ent>⟦br⟧
